---
const stats = [
  { value: '2024–26', label: 'BTS CIEL' },
  { value: '3',       label: 'serveurs en lab' },
  { value: '18+',     label: 'certifications' },
  { value: 'MICSI',   label: 'Mastère CESI visé' },
];
---

<section id="about" class="py-28">
  <div class="section-container">

    <div class="reveal mb-14">
      <p class="section-label">// qui suis-je</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">À propos</h2>
      <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-500 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-14 items-start">

      <!-- Avatar + badges -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 reveal reveal-delay-1 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start gap-7">
        <div class="w-44 h-44 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-600/20 to-indigo-600/20 border border-violet-500/20 flex items-center justify-center shadow-glow-violet">
          <span class="font-mono text-5xl font-black gradient-text">PP</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          {['Curieux', 'Autodidacte', 'Orienté pratique'].map(trait => (
            <span class="chip text-sm">{trait}</span>
          ))}
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-base text-slate-400">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-violet-400 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" />
          </svg>
          Ariège, France
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio + stats -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 reveal reveal-delay-2 flex flex-col gap-9">

        <div class="space-y-5 text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Titulaire du <span class="text-violet-300 font-medium">BTS CIEL option A</span>
            (Lycée de Mirepoix, 2024–2026), je me spécialise dans l'infrastructure,
            les réseaux et la cybersécurité. Objectif à terme :
            <span class="text-violet-300 font-medium">Infrastructure / Cybersecurity Manager</span>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Cet été, je suis en CDD chez <span class="text-slate-200 font-medium">Alsatis Services</span>
            (Verniolle) comme technicien support N1/N2 avant de démarrer le
            <span class="text-violet-300 font-medium">Bachelor ASR</span> puis le
            <span class="text-violet-300 font-medium">Mastère MICSI</span> au CESI, en alternance.
          </p>
          <p>
            J'entretiens un <span class="text-slate-200 font-medium">home-lab actif</span>
            (Dell R610 + Asus F540LJ sous Proxmox) où je déploie et teste en conditions réelles :
            SIEM Wazuh, Active Directory, PKI, Zero Trust.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {stats.map(stat => (
            <div class="glow-card rounded-xl p-5 bg-bg-card text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-black gradient-text-violet">{stat.value}</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-1 leading-tight">{stat.label}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Current status -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-5 rounded-xl bg-violet-500/8 border border-violet-500/20">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-violet-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-base text-slate-300">
            <span class="text-violet-300 font-semibold">En ce moment :</span> CDD technicien support N1/N2 chez Alsatis Services (juillet–septembre 2026),
            puis démarrage du Bachelor ASR au CESI en alternance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
